<i>noun</i>: 흡인 [흐빈], 흡수성 [흡쑤썽], 흡수 [흡쑤], 열중 [열쭝], 몰입 [모립], 몰두 [몰뚜], 골몰 [골몰] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square"><li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>흡인 [흐빈]</dt><br>
<dd>absorption; suction; attraction</dd><br>
<dd>빨아들이거나 끌어당김.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of sucking or attracting something.</dd><br>
<dt>흡수성 [흡쑤썽]</dt><br>
<dd>absorptiveness; absorption</dd><br>
<dd>빨아들이는 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>The property of absorbing something.</dd><br>
<dt>흡수 [흡쑤]</dt><br>
<dd>1. absorption; intake</dd><br>
<dd>안이나 속으로 빨아들임.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of drawing in or inhaling something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. absorption</dd><br>
<dd>외부에 있는 사람이나 사물 등을 내부로 모여들게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making a person or thing come into a certain place.</dd><br>
<dt>열중 [열쭝]</dt><br>
<dd>absorption; immersion</dd><br>
<dd>한 가지 일에 정신을 집중함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of concentrating on something.</dd><br>
<dt>몰입 [모립]</dt><br>
<dd>immersion; absorption</dd><br>
<dd>다른 일에 관심을 가지지 않고 한 가지 일에만 집중하여 깊이 빠짐.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of focusing solely on one thing, being deeply involved in it without paying any attention to other affairs.</dd><br>
<dt>몰두 [몰뚜]</dt><br>
<dd>absorption</dd><br>
<dd>다른 일에 관심을 가지지 않고 한 가지 일에만 집중함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of focusing on one thing without taking interest in anything else.</dd><br>
<dt>골몰 [골몰]</dt><br>
<dd>preoccupation; absorption</dd><br>
<dd>한 가지 일이나 생각에만 집중함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of concentrating on only one thing or thought.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>